flowchart LR
  subgraph Control_Areas
    CA1[Identity & Permission Controls]
    CA2[Retrieval Authorization Controls]
    CA3[Tool/MCP Authorization Controls]
    CA4[Observability & Evidence Controls]
  end

  CA1 --> E1[permissions.py / auth users & keys]
  CA2 --> E2[document_access.py / query filters]
  CA3 --> E3[tool api + mcp api + tool_runner]
  CA4 --> E4[logger + tracing + metrics + evidence artifacts]

  E1 --> ST1[Partially Confirmed]
  E2 --> ST2[Confirmed (static path)]
  E3 --> ST3[Needs Verification]
  E4 --> ST4[Partially Confirmed / Unknown at decision granularity]
